description:
Step-by-step instructions to install your 13.6 Tesla-style 13.6" Android  screen (SquareWheels G-Series, MK7, MK6, or MK5) head unit on the Infiniti Q50/Q60.  

It's really easy - NO NEED TO CUT INTO STEERING COLUMN like the other Tesla screens!

G-Series MARK 7 is now available for sale! Check it out:
https://youtu.be/mp3OE77U0AY

BUY NOW:
https://squarewheelsauto.com/products/new-aucar-mark6-tesla-style-screen-for-infiniti-q50-q60-mk6

Here's the best place to mount the GPS antenna - it should have a view of the sky: https://youtu.be/qVZdVurUr1Y

BUY ME A COFFEE/BEER:
https://www.buymeacoffee.com/squarewheels

HIT ME ON IG:
